trans-unit.source: Serves as the base class for all zone controls that act as catalogs.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som basisklasse for alle zone-kontroller som fungerer som kataloger.

trans-unit.source: Catalogs contain lists of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls that users can add to a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Kataloger inneholde lister med <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller som brukere kan legge til en webside.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogZoneBase class is a base class that inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone> class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CatalogZoneBase er en basisklasse som arver fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone>

trans-unit.source: It provides a base set of behaviors for derived zones.
trans-unit.target: Det gir et grunnleggende sett med virkemåter for avledede soner.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogZoneBase class provides a unique user interface (UI) that enables users to add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls and other server controls to Web pages.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CatalogZoneBase inneholder en unik brukergrensesnittet (UI) som gjør det mulig å legge til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller og andre serverkontroller til websider.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Controls that derive from the CatalogZoneBase class, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>, are the controls actually placed on Web pages.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller som som er avledet fra klassen CatalogZoneBase <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>, er kontrollene faktisk montert på nettsider.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>

trans-unit.source: They act as containers for other controls, known as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, that create lists of server controls for users to add to a page.
trans-unit.target: De fungerer som beholdere for andre kontroller kjent som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller, som oppretter lister over serverkontroller for brukerne å legge til en side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Zones that derive from the CatalogZoneBase class can appear only when the page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: Soner som er avledet fra klassen CatalogZoneBase kan vises bare når siden er i visningsmodus for katalogen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A CatalogZoneBase zone can contain only <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, and conversely, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can reside only in CatalogZoneBase zones.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En CatalogZoneBase sone kan bare inneholde <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller, og derimot <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller kan ligge i CatalogZoneBase soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The mechanism for adding server controls to a catalog is the following set of three controls that derive from the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Mekanisme for å legge til serverkontroller i en katalog er følgende sett med tre kontroller som er avledet fra base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: |Control|Description| |-------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>|Maintains references to controls that have been closed on a page.
trans-unit.target: | Kontrollen | Beskrivelse | |-------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>| Opprettholder referanser til kontroller som har blitt lukket på en side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: These controls can be reopened (added back to the page) by users.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>|Contains references to controls that are declared in a Web Parts catalog in the markup of a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Disse kontrollene kan åpnes på nytt (tillagt tilbake til siden) av brukere. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>| Inneholder referanser til kontroller som er angitt i en katalog for webdeler i koden for en webside.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: These controls can be added to a Web page by users.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>|Provides the UI for a user to upload a definition file to a catalog so that the control can be added to a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Disse kontroller kan legges til en webside av brukere. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>| Gir Brukergrensesnittet for brukere å laste opp en fil i en katalog slik at kontrollen kan legges til en webside.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Definition files are XML file with a .WebPart file name extension that import settings for a control.
trans-unit.target: Av definisjonsfilene er XML-fil med en. Webdelen filtype som importere innstillinger for en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The control must be present on the server before the definition file can be imported.| The CatalogZoneBase class has a number of properties that are useful for displaying catalogs of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen må være installert på serveren før definisjonsfilen kan importeres. | Klassen CatalogZoneBase har flere egenskaper som er nyttige for å vise kataloger for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.AddVerb%2A> property references the verb that adds a selected control from the catalog to the page, while the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A> property references a verb that closes the catalog and returns the page's display mode to browse mode.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.AddVerb%2A>egenskapen refererer verb som legger til en kontroll fra katalogen siden, mens den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A>egenskapen refererer til et verb som lukker katalogen, og returnerer sidens visningsmodus for å bla gjennom-modus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.AddVerb%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogParts%2A> property references the collection of all <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogParts%2A>egenskapen refererer til samlingen av alle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: Several text-oriented properties, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.EmptyZoneText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.HeaderText%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.InstructionText%2A>, override base properties to provide default text appropriate for catalogs.
trans-unit.target: Flere tekstbaserte egenskaper som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.EmptyZoneText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.HeaderText%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.InstructionText%2A>, overstyre base egenskaper for å angi standardtekst til kataloger.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.InstructionText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.HeaderText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.EmptyZoneText%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectTargetZoneText%2A> property contains the text alongside the drop-down list control that allows users to choose which zone a control will be added to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectTargetZoneText%2A>egenskapen inneholder ved siden av rullegardinlisten kontrollen som tillater at brukere velger hvilken sone en kontroll legges til.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectTargetZoneText%2A>

trans-unit.source: Several other properties are included in the CatalogZoneBase class.
trans-unit.target: Flere egenskaper er inkludert i CatalogZoneBase-klassen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedCatalogPartID%2A> property is a unique string identifier for the currently selected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedCatalogPartID%2A>egenskapen er en unik strengidentifikatoren for den valgte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedCatalogPartID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.ShowCatalogIcons%2A> property indicates whether to show the icons that can be associated with controls by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A> property on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.ShowCatalogIcons%2A>egenskapen angir om du vil vise ikonene som kan knyttes til kontroller ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>egenskap i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.ShowCatalogIcons%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A> property contains style attributes for the links to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls that are not currently selected in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A>egenskapen inneholder Stilattributter for koblinger til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller som ikke er valgt i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: In contrast, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A> property contains style attributes for a link to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control that the user has currently selected in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligning av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A>egenskapen inneholder Stilattributter for en kobling til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll som brukeren har for øyeblikket er valgt i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: In addition to the properties, there are also some methods in the CatalogZoneBase class, in addition to the standard event-handling and rendering methods inherited from other base controls, which are uniquely designed for the purpose of handling catalogs of controls.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg til egenskapene det også noen metoder i klassen CatalogZoneBase, i tillegg til den standard hendelseshåndtering og gjengivelse metoder arvet fra andre base kontroller, som er unikt utformet for å håndtere kataloger kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A> method creates the chrome (peripheral UI elements such as a border, verbs, icons, and a title) that surrounds each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control in the zone, and also handles the rendering for the controls.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A>metoden oppretter chrome (eksterne UI-elementene som en kantlinje, verb, ikonene og en tittel) som omgir hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen i sonen, og behandler også gjengivelse av kontrollene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A> method is an abstract method; derived classes override it to create instances of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls contained in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A>metoden er en abstrakt; avledede klasser overstyre den for å opprette forekomster av alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.InvalidateCatalogParts%2A> method can be called by a derived class if the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the zone changes for some programmatic reason, and the derived class needs to recreate the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.InvalidateCatalogParts%2A>metoder kan kalles med en utledede klassen hvis samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller sone endringer for noen programmatisk årsak og den utledede klassen må gjenopprette samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.InvalidateCatalogParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.LoadPostData%2A> method loads the previously existing state for the check boxes next to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls in the catalog, whenever the page is posted back to the server; conversely, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SaveControlState%2A> method saves the state of the check boxes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.LoadPostData%2A>metoden laster inn den tidligere eksisterende tilstanden for avmerkingsboksene ved siden av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller i katalogen, når siden posteres tilbake til serveren; derimot den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SaveControlState%2A>metoden lagrer tilstanden avmerkingsboksene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SaveControlState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.LoadPostData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.RenderCatalogPartLinks%2A> method provides all the rendering for the links to each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control contained in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.RenderCatalogPartLinks%2A>metoden gir alle gjengivelse for koblinger til hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.RenderCatalogPartLinks%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes the class for use by an inherited class instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer klasse for bruk av en arvet klasse-forekomst.

trans-unit.source: This constructor can only be called by an inherited class.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren, kan bare kalles med en arvet klasse.

trans-unit.source: The constructor is called when a derived class is initialized, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> class provided with the Web Parts control set.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren kalles når en utledede klassen er initialisert, som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>klassen som er angitt med webdeler kontrollen settet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>

trans-unit.source: The base CatalogZoneBase constructor helps prepare the page to display the Web Parts catalog user interface (UI), by passing the appropriate <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Grunnleggende CatalogZoneBase konstruktøren bidrar til å klargjøre siden for å vise webdeler katalogen-brukergrensesnittet (UI), ved å sende den riktige <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: Specifically, the constructor passes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode> object.
trans-unit.target: Nærmere bestemt konstruktøren formidler en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> object that enables end users to add controls from a catalog to a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> objektet som gir sluttbrukerne mulighet til å legge til kontroller fra en katalog i en webdeler-siden.

trans-unit.source: The add verb is referenced by the AddVerb property on a control derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> class.
trans-unit.target: Legg til verbet refererer til egenskapen AddVerb i en kontroll som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: The add verb adds a control that an end user has selected in the catalog to a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Legg til verbet legger til en kontroll som sluttbrukeren i katalogen til en webside er valgt.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the add verb appears in the user interface (UI) as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> control, although it can also be a link or an image.
trans-unit.target: Legg til verbet vanligvis vises i brukergrensesnittet (UI) som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>kontrollere, selv om det kan også være en kobling eller et bilde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>

trans-unit.source: The add verb is a zone-level control, meaning that although there might be several <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the catalog, the add verb applies to all the controls selected by the user and adds them to the selected zone.
trans-unit.target: Legg til verbet er en sone tilgangskontroll, betyr at selv om det er kanskje flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i katalogen, Legg til verbet gjelder for alle kontrollene som er valgt av brukeren, og legger dem til valgt sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> that enables end users to add controls from the catalog to a Web page.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> som gjør det mulig for sluttbrukerne mulighet til å legge til kontroller fra katalogen i en webside.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"></xref> class associated with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"> </xref> klassen som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A> method is called, it creates one instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome> class, and this instance is used to render the peripheral user interface (UI) elements (also called the chrome) for all <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in a zone.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A>-metoden, opprettes en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome>klassen, og denne forekomsten brukes til å gjengi eksterne brukeren elementer i brukergrensesnittet (UI) (også kalt chrome) for alle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A>

trans-unit.source: The chrome elements for an individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control include its border and title text.
trans-unit.target: Chrome-elementer for en person <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen inkluderer teksten kantlinje og tittel.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls provided with the Web Parts control set do not have header verbs by default.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollene gav webdeler kontrollen settet har ingen hodet verb som standard.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"></xref> that is associated with the zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"> </xref> som er knyttet til sonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls contained in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av alle de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogParts property provides a reference to a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CatalogParts inneholder en referanse til en samling av alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: It references both the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls provided with the Web Parts control set, and any custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls that are added to the zone.
trans-unit.target: Den refererer til både den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller gav webdeler kontrollen settet og en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller som er lagt til i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The collection is initially created when another method accesses the CatalogParts property, and the property calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen opprettes opprinnelig når en annen metode har tilgang til egenskapen CatalogParts og egenskapen kaller den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A>

trans-unit.target: Kaller ganske enkelt den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen skal returneres websiden for å bla gjennom-modus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> object that enables end users to close the catalog user interface (UI) and return the page to normal browse mode.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> objektet som gir sluttbrukerne mulighet til å lukke katalogen-brukergrensesnittet (UI) og gå tilbake siden normal lesemodus.

trans-unit.source: The close verb is referenced by the CloseVerb property on a control derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> class.
trans-unit.target: Lukk verbet refererer til egenskapen CloseVerb i en kontroll som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: User can click the close verb in the zone footer.
trans-unit.target: Brukeren kan klikke Lukk verbet i sone bunnteksten.

trans-unit.source: When the user clicks the close verb, any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls the user has selected are ignored, the catalog UI closes, and the page returns to normal browse mode.
trans-unit.target: Når brukeren klikker Lukk verbet alle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller brukeren har valgt ignoreres, katalogen Brukergrensesnittet lukkes, og returnerer siden normal lesemodus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The close verb is a zone-level control, meaning that its action applies at the level of the whole zone.
trans-unit.target: Lukk verbet er en sone tilgangskontroll, noe som betyr at handlingen gjelder på nivå i hele sonen.

trans-unit.source: When a user clicks the close verb, any controls that have been selected but not added to the page are ignored, the catalog is closed, and the page returns to browse mode.
trans-unit.target: Når en bruker klikker Lukk verbet, kontroller som er valgt, men ikke lagt til i siden ignoreres, katalogen lukkes, og returnerer siden for å bla gjennom-modus.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> that enables end users to close the catalog UI on the Web page.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> som kan sluttbrukerne lukke katalogen Brukergrensesnittet på siden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls provided with the Web Parts control set do not have header verbs by default.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollene gav webdeler kontrollen settet har ingen hodet verb som standard.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: However, it is possible to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeState%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, so that you can minimize and restore the control programmatically if needed.
trans-unit.target: Det er mulig å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeState%2A>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollere, slik at du kan redusere og gjenopprette kontrollen programmatisk om nødvendig.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeState%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"></xref> that renders the peripheral UI elements for the zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"> </xref> som gjengir av eksterne UI-elementene for sonen.

trans-unit.source: Provides a base method declaration that derived zones can override to handle the details of creating the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls contained in a zone.
trans-unit.target: Gir en base Metodedeklarasjon som avledet soner kan overstyre til å behandle detaljene for oppretting av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller i en sone.

trans-unit.source: The CreateCatalogParts method provides no implementation.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateCatalogParts gir ingen implementering.

trans-unit.source: It is intended to be implemented in a derived class, and should be used to create an instance of the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls contained in a zone, whenever the hosting Web page enters catalog mode.
trans-unit.target: Det er ment å være implementert i den utledede klassen, og skal brukes til å opprette en forekomst av samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en sone, når verts websiden angir katalogmodus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.CreateCatalogParts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method provides one example of an implementation of the CreateCatalogParts method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.CreateCatalogParts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden gir et eksempel på en implementering av metoden CreateCatalogParts.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.CreateCatalogParts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Note that any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> that is added to the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in an implementation of the CreateCatalogParts method must have a value assigned to its ID property, otherwise an exception will be thrown when the collection is assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Legg merke til at <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>som er lagt til i samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en implementering av metoden CreateCatalogParts må ha en verdi som er tilordnet til egenskapen ID, ellers vil bli utløst et unntak under samlingen er tilordnet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogParts%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The method can create the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls from several sources: controls that are declared in persistence format within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> control, or controls that are persisted in various storage mechanisms, such as an XML file or a database.
trans-unit.target: Metoden kan opprette den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller fra flere kilder: Kontroller som er angitt i utholdenhet format i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>kontrollen eller kontrollene er fast i forskjellige lagring mekanismer, for eksempel en XML-fil eller en database.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartCollection"> </xref> som inneholder samlingen av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> Kontroller tilknyttet sonen.

trans-unit.target: Strengverdien for egenskapen EmptyZoneText vises når en webside går inn i katalogmodus, hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sonen inneholder ingen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: A string containing the message that appears in an empty zone.
trans-unit.target: En streng med meldingen som vises i en tom sone.

trans-unit.source: A default culture-specific string is supplied by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En standard kultur-spesifikke streng er angitt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten for toppteksten for en sone.

trans-unit.target: Strengverdien for egenskapen HeaderText vises i toppteksten for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone, som er på toppen av sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: The text of the HeaderText property is displayed when a page enters catalog mode and the catalog user interface (UI) becomes visible.
trans-unit.target: Teksten for egenskapen HeaderText vises når en side angir katalogmodus og katalogen-brukergrensesnittet (UI) blir synlig.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the header text for the zone.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder toppteksten for sonen.

trans-unit.source: A default culture-specific string is supplied by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En standard kultur-spesifikke streng er angitt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text in a zone that provides directions for end users.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten i en sone som gir retninger for sluttbrukere.

trans-unit.target: Strengverdien for egenskapen InstructionText vises bare under toppteksten for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: The text of the InstructionText property is displayed when a page enters catalog mode and the catalog user interface (UI) becomes visible.
trans-unit.target: Teksten for egenskapen InstructionText vises når en side angir katalogmodus og katalogen-brukergrensesnittet (UI) blir synlig.

trans-unit.source: The purpose of the InstructionText property is to provide the user with general instructions on what to do when the catalog UI is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Formålet med egenskapen InstructionText er å gi brukeren mer informasjon om hva du skal gjøre når katalogen Brukergrensesnittet vises.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the directions for end users.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder instruksjonene for sluttbrukere.

trans-unit.source: A default, culture-specific string is provided by the Web Parts control set.
trans-unit.target: Standard kultur-spesifikke streng er angitt med de webdeler kontrollen.

trans-unit.target: Ødelegger samlingen av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> Kontroller knyttet til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.target: InvalidateCatalogParts metoder kan kalles av avledede klasser Hvis listen over <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller knyttet til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone er endret for noen årsaken, og den utledede klassen må få en oppdatert liste over <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The derived class should first call InvalidateCatalogParts to destroy the current collection, and then the base class will call <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A> as needed to create the updated collection.
trans-unit.target: Den utledede klassen må først kalle InvalidateCatalogParts Hvis du vil fjerne den gjeldende samlingen, og deretter basisklassen ringe <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A>etter behov for å opprette den oppdaterte samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: When a user clicks one of the links, the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control becomes the selected control, and the child controls contained by that selected control become visible.
trans-unit.target: Når brukeren klikker en av koblingene for den tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen blir den valgte kontrollen, og de underordnede kontrollene finnes i den valgte kontrollen blir synlige.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> object referenced by the PartLinkStyle property contains the style attributes for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls that are not currently selected.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objektet refererer til egenskapen PartLinkStyle inneholder stil attributtene for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller som ikke er valgt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: Although the object referenced by the property is read-only, you can still use it to set the underlying style characteristics for the unselected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Selv om objektet refererer til egenskapen er skrivebeskyttet, kan du fortsatt bruke den til å angi underliggende stilen for den ikke er merket <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> that contains style attributes for the controls that are not currently selected.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> som inneholder Stilattributter for kolonner som ikke er valgt.

trans-unit.source: Carries out the actions associated with one of the zone verbs, or raises an event that posts back to the server.
trans-unit.target: Utfører handlingene som er knyttet til én av zone-verbene, eller viser en hendelsen som legger inn på serveren.

trans-unit.source: If the `eventArgument` parameter data indicates that the add verb or the close verb was clicked, then the RaisePostBackEvent method carries out the action associated with the verb, such as adding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls to the page, or closing the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `eventArgument` parameterdata indikerer at verbet Legg til eller avsluttende verbet ble klikket og metoden RaisePostBackEvent utfører handlingen som er forbundet med verbet, for eksempel legge til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller siden eller lukke katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If the method is being called for any other reason, then the base method is invoked to raise a postback event to the server.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden kalles av andre årsaker, aktiveres metoden base for å tilbakesending til serveren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the argument for the event.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder argumentet for hendelsen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Renders the zone to the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelser sonen til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.Render%2A> method overrides the base method from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> class to call the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.VerifyRenderingInServerForm%2A> method, which verifies that an HTML form is rendered for the zone control at run time.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.Render%2A>metoden overstyrer metoden base fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>klassen for å kalle den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.VerifyRenderingInServerForm%2A>metoden som bekrefter at et HTML-skjema gjengis for zone-kontroll på kjøretidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page.VerifyRenderingInServerForm%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.Render%2A>

trans-unit.source: After the verification, the method then renders the remaining contents of the zone.
trans-unit.target: Etter bekreftelse gjengir metoden deretter gjenværende innholdet i sonen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that receives the zone's content.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som mottar i sonen innhold.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the base method to render the body area of a zone derived from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer metoden base for å gjengi området brødteksten i en sone som er avledet fra den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The RenderBody method renders the body area of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone, which is the main content area between the header and footer areas and contains <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RenderBody gjengir området brødteksten i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone, som er den primære innhold mellom topp- og bunntekst områder og inneholder <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: The RenderBody method overrides the base method in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone> class to provide specialized rendering that addresses layout and style attributes that apply only to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zones.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RenderBody overstyrer base metoden i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>klassen for å angi spesialiserte gjengivelse som løser oppsett og stil attributter som bare gjelder <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>

trans-unit.source: The method renders a table that contains the entire contents of the body, and within that table, it sets different attribute values depending on various conditions, including how many <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls are in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Metoden gjengir en tabell som inneholder hele innholdet i meldingsteksten og i tabellen, setter annen attributtverdier basert på forskjellige betingelser, inkludert hvor mange <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller er i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: If there are multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, a link is created for each control, and only the contents of the currently selected control are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller, opprettes en kobling for hver kontroll, og bare innholdet i den valgte kontrollen skal vises.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Special style attributes are set in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogPartChrome%2A> property for the selected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control versus the ones that are not currently selected.
trans-unit.target: Spesiell Stilattributter som er angitt den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogPartChrome%2A>egenskapen for den valgte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen sammenlignet med de som ikke er valgt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CatalogPartChrome%2A>

trans-unit.source: If there are no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in the zone, the RenderBody method renders the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EmptyZoneText%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes ingen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i sonen, metoden RenderBody gjengir verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EmptyZoneText%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EmptyZoneText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that receives the zone's body content.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som mottar i sonen brødtekst innhold.

trans-unit.source: Renders the links to the individual <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelser koblingene til individuelle <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: The RenderCatalogPartLinks method renders links to the individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in a zone if there are multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RenderCatalogPartLinks gjengir koblinger for vedkommende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollerer i en sone Hvis det finnes flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The link for the currently selected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is rendered differently so that it stands out from the unselected controls.
trans-unit.target: Koblingen for den valgte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen gjengis forskjellig slik at det vises fra umerket kontrollene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Developers can set the style attributes for the selected and unselected control links by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A> properties, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Utviklere kan angi attributtene stilen for valgt og ikke valgt kontrollen koblingene ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A>Egenskaper henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The links to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in a zone are not navigational; they are for displaying the user interface (UI) of the controls.
trans-unit.target: Koblingene til de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i en sone er ikke navigering; de er for å vise brukergrensesnittet (UI) vises.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: When a user clicks the link for a control, the UI for any other displayed control is hidden, and the UI for the selected control is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Når en bruker klikker koblingen for en kontroll, Brukergrensesnittet for alle viste kontroller er skjult og Brukergrensesnittet for den valgte kontrollen skal vises.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that receives the contents of the links to the zone's controls.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som mottar innholdet i koblinger til i sonen kontroller.

trans-unit.source: Renders the footer area for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelser bunntekstområdet for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: The footer of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone is the bottom area of the zone that contains the zone-level verbs such as the add verb and the close verb.
trans-unit.target: Bunnteksten på en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sonen er det nederste området i sonen som inneholder sone nivå verb som verbet Legg til og lukk verbet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: In the underlying markup, a footer is simply a cell in an HTML table.
trans-unit.target: I den underliggende markup er bunntekst bare en celle i en HTML-tabell.

trans-unit.source: The RenderFooter method first creates the style attributes for the footer, and then calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.RenderVerbs%2A> method to render the add and close verbs.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RenderFooter først oppretter attributtene stilen for bunnteksten, og kaller deretter den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.RenderVerbs%2A>metoden gjengi Legg til for å lukke verb.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.RenderVerbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that renders the footer area for the zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som gjengir bunntekstområdet for sonen.

trans-unit.source: Renders the verbs in the footer area of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelser verb i bunntekstområdet i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: The RenderVerbs method renders the add verb and the close verb within the footer area of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RenderVerbs gjengir verbet Legg til og lukk verbet i bunntekstområdet i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that renders the verbs for the zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som gjengir verb for sonen.

trans-unit.source: Saves any changes in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> control's state that occur after the Web page is posted back to the server.
trans-unit.target: Lagrer endringer i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> kontrollens tilstand som kan oppstå når Web-siden posteres tilbake til serveren.

trans-unit.source: The SaveControlState method is concerned with state data that is essential for a control's operation (such as an index or keyword) and is separate from the control's view-state data.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SaveControlState er opptatt med tilstandsdata som er viktige for en kontroll operasjonen (for eksempel en indeks eller nøkkelordet) og er atskilt fra kontrollens visningsstatus data.

trans-unit.source: The method first calls the base method to save the existing state data for the control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden base for å lagre de eksisterende Tilstandsdataene for kontrollen metodekall først.

trans-unit.source: Next, it determines whether a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control in the zone is currently selected, by checking whether the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedCatalogPartID%2A> property has a value.
trans-unit.target: Neste bestemmer om en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen i sonen er valgt, ved å kontrollere om det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedCatalogPartID%2A>egenskapen har en verdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedCatalogPartID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: If there is a selected control, the method updates the existing state data with the state data from the selected control, and then returns all the state data.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er en kontroll, metoden oppdaterer eksisterende tilstandsdata med tilstandsdata fra den valgte kontrollen, og returnerer statusen for alle dataene.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that contains the state data for the control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som inneholder Tilstandsdataene for kontrollen.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: If there have been no changes to the state, the method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen endringer i tilstanden, returneres <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Saves any view-state changes that have occurred after a page was posted back to the server.
trans-unit.target: Lagrer endringer visningsstatus som oppstod etter at en side ble posteres tilbake til serveren.

trans-unit.source: The SaveViewState method calls the base method to save the view state associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: SaveViewState metodekall metoden base for å lagre visningsstatusen som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: Next, it saves any view state for the add and close verbs, as well as for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> objects associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Neste sparer noen visningsstatusen for å legge til og lukk verb, og den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objekter som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: Returns the zone control's current view state.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer sone kontrollens gjeldende visningsstatus.

trans-unit.source: If no view state is associated with the zone, this method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen visningsstatus er knyttet til sonen, metoden returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string as an identifier for the currently selected <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control in a zone.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en streng som en identifikator for den valgte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontroll i en sone.

trans-unit.source: The SelectedCatalogPartID property allows you to set an identifier of your choice for the currently selected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SelectedCatalogPartID kan du angi en identifikator for valget for den valgte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: This does not change the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> property value, so you can use this property for your own programmatic purposes.
trans-unit.target: Dette endrer ikke kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>egenskapsverdien, så du kan bruke denne egenskapen til dine egne programmatisk formål.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you wanted to always carry out some programmatic action on the currently selected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, this property enables you to access that control through a known value that you set in advance.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du alltid vil utføre noe programmatisk på den valgte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll, denne egenskapen kan du få tilgang til denne kontrollen gjennom en kjent verdi som du angir på forhånd.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan ikke angis ved oppsett eller stil arket Oppsett.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> and [ASP.NET Themes and Skins](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute>og [ASP.NET tema og skallene](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: A string that serves as the identifier for the currently selected control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som fungerer som identifikatoren for den valgte kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The default is the value of the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID*> property.
trans-unit.target: Standard er verdien for kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID*>

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that contains style attributes for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control that is currently selected in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Henter et objekt som inneholder stilen attributtene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontrollen som er valgt i sonen.

trans-unit.source: In a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone, links are displayed for each type of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>.
trans-unit.target: I en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone, vises koblingene for hver type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: When a user clicks one of the links, the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control becomes the selected control, and the child controls contained by that selected control become visible.
trans-unit.target: Når brukeren klikker en av koblingene for den tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen blir den valgte kontrollen, og de underordnede kontrollene finnes i den valgte kontrollen blir synlige.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> object referenced by the SelectedPartLinkStyle property contains the style attributes of the link for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control that is currently selected.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objektet refererer til egenskapen SelectedPartLinkStyle inneholder attributtene stilen for koblingen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen som er valgt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: Although the object referenced by the property is read-only, you can still use it to set the underlying style characteristics for the selected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Selv om objektet refererer til egenskapen er skrivebeskyttet, kan du fortsatt bruke den til å angi underliggende stilen for den valgte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> that contains style attributes for the control that is currently selected.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> som inneholder stilen attributtene for kontrollen som er valgt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text alongside the control in the catalog user interface (UI) that allows users to choose which zone to add their selected controls to.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten ved siden av kontrollen i katalogen-brukergrensesnittet (UI) som tillater at brukere velger hvilke sone for å legge til de valgte kontrollene til.

trans-unit.source: When the catalog UI first appears, users can select one of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>, that contains <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or other server controls that can be added to the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når katalogen Brukergrensesnittet vises først, kan brukerne velge ett av de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>, som inneholder <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>eller andre serverkontroller som kan legges til nettsiden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The user selects one or more controls, and can then use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DropDownList> control in the footer area of the catalog and choose the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> control on the page in which to place the selected server controls.
trans-unit.target: Brukeren velger én eller flere kontroller, og kan deretter bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DropDownList>kontrollere i bunntekstområdet i katalogen, og velg den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontroll på siden for å plassere de valgte serverkontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DropDownList>

trans-unit.source: The text value of the SelectTargetZoneText property is displayed alongside the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DropDownList> control as a simple instruction.
trans-unit.target: Tekstverdien for egenskapen SelectTargetZoneText vises ved siden av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DropDownList>kontrollen som en enkel instruksjon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DropDownList>

trans-unit.source: The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen Hvis du velger, kan lagres automatisk på en ressursfil ved hjelp av en designer verktøyet.

trans-unit.target: En standard kultur-spesifikke streng er angitt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether server controls in the catalog display their associated icons in the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om serverkontroller i katalogen vise de tilhørende ikonene i katalogen.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is the URL to an image that is used as an icon to represent the control in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen er URL-adressen til et bilde som brukes som et ikon til å representere kontrollen i en katalog for kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The ShowCatalogIcons property indicates whether the icons associated with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> and other server controls are displayed in the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ShowCatalogIcons angir om ikonene knyttet til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>og andre serverkontroller vises i katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.target: Sporer endres til en zone-kontroll visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.source: The TrackViewState method first calls the base method in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone> class to track the view state associated with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Metoden TrackViewState kaller først base-metoden den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone>klassen for å spore visningsstatusen som er tilknyttet en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZone>

trans-unit.source: Next, the method begins tracking the view state for the add and close verbs, as well as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> objects associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.PartLinkStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.SelectedPartLinkStyle%2A> properties.
